# CDK build artefacts
cdk.out/
# cdk.context.json caches AWS-API lookups (AZ list, AMI IDs) for
# reproducible synth. It contains the AWS account ID, which we keep
# out of git history as a defensive default — `cdk synth` re-fetches
# on first use per operator.
